        9jastay provides powerful tools that make discovering, booking, and managing
        accommodation across Nigeria simple, secure, and reliable.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="box">
          <h5>Smart Property Search</h5>
